name: Tom Holland
description:
Improved and enhanced v2.0

It works on any realistic model with a normal negative prompt. A weight around 1.0 works fine from my tests. A CFG weight around 5-7 works great depending upon the prompts. See the examples for the various comparisons.

Note:

  • Triggers with tom holland.

  • Use any realistic model to achieve the sample images

  • Add in negative prompt: Child, childish

  • Feedbacks and suggestions is highly encouraged

  • Share your prompts! I wanna see your own creations!

Share your generated here with other model. Comments and feedbacks is highly appreciated :))))

modelVersions.description:
What's New?

  • Improved Version of v1.0

  • Trained with 400 images with 10 max epoch

  • Configured and fixed child like features

  • Sample images are now similar with the subject

  • Added new poses and expressions

Note:

  • Add in negative prompt: Child, childish

  • Feedbacks and suggestions is highly encouraged

  • Share your prompts! I wanna see your own creations!
